name: White Holiday Set of 5 Cards
description:
99 percent inspired is our ongoing photo project where we document our travels around the world- some of which we post on our instagram feed ;-)

For the holidays, we have created limited edition photo card sets of mixed images taken in Austria, Vienna, Prague and Budapest at Holiday time. 

5 individual images on 4x6" cards with white envelopes. 
Satin coated on the outside, the inside is left uncoated, 
making it easier for you to write your own message.
